  "title" : "How do you know a variable type in java?",
  "body" : "<p>Let's say I declare a variable:</p>\n\n<pre><code>String a = \"test\";\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>And I want to know what type it is, i.e., the output should be <code>java.lang.String</code> How do I do this?</p>\n"
